'''Munto''' was a large city on [[Commenor/Legends|Commenor]] located near [[Kliffen]]. It was built primarily in the midst of a [[Munto valley|valley]] with houses built on the terraces; the city played host to moderate [[Airspeeder/Legends|airspeeder]] and [[Landspeeder/Legends|landspeeder]] traffic. It was home to the [[Annual Mid-Rim Domesticated Sub-Sentient Show]] and was near the [[Xenovet]] site.

